{"about_the_game":"Peel, jump, swap - Embark on a grand sticky adventure with Perin!<br>Help Perin, the protagonist of this story, travel a world plunged into stickery-madness brought upon a witch's mischief in a puzzle-action game depicting their legacy.<br><br>The key to strategy in this game is &quot;how&quot; you interact with the stickers.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Slow-peel</h2>Bend the stickers to your will by slowly peeling it off from the corners!<br>It might even create new platforms to step on...?<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006350/extras/hagasu.gif?t=1727406094\" /><br>Change the order on how the stickers are placed!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006350/extras/irekaeru.gif?t=1727406094\" /><br>By reforming the stickers, maybe the path forward might just unveil themselves..?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Power-peel</h2>Rip the stickers off with one swift move by storing power!<br>It might create enough force to do a bigger jump if you're on it..?<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006350/extras/tobu.gif?t=1727406094\" /><br>Enemies layered on top won't stand a chance against it!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006350/extras/ikkinihagasu.gif?t=1727406094\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Estimated total play time</h2>2 and a half hours - 3 hours<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006350/extras/boss.gif?t=1727406094\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"\u521d\u3081\u3066\u306e\u30da\u30ea\u30f3","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3006350/9fe57da26e028d7541011f3aaf10526c4ac3160e.jpg"},{"name":"\u304d\u3087\u3046\u3066\u304d\u30c9\u30f3\u30fb\u30d9\u30ea\u30b9","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/s